citation: Taxation and Related Legislation (Miscellaneous Amendments) Act (No. 2) 2008 (Repealed) (Tas)
text:
Taxation and Related Legislation (Miscellaneous Amendments) Act (No. 2) 2008 (Repealed)

1. (Repealed)
    The Taxation and Related Legislation (Miscellaneous Amendments) Act (No. 2) 2008 has been repealed by Schedule 1 to the Redundant Legislation Repeal Act 2016
